ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  "sparql_query": "PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX a223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX a223sb: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/si-builder#>\\n\\nSELECT ?zoneLabel ?propLabel ?endpoint ?mpcName ?alcLabel\\nWHERE {\\n  # Zones (PhysicalSpace)\\n  ?zone a a223:PhysicalSpace .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel . }\\n\\n  # Connection points attached to a zone (any type  often ZoneConnectionPoint)\\n  ?zone a223:hasConnectionPoint ?cp .\\n\\n  # Properties associated with the connection point\\n  ?cp a223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .\\n\\n  # Keep only nonwritable properties (writable not true)\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS {\\n    ?prop brick:writable ?w .\\n    FILTER(?w = \\"True\\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string>)\\n  }\\n\\n  # ALC endpoint reference (external reference whose label mentions ALC)\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?prop a223:hasExternalReference ?ext .\\n    ?ext rdfs:label ?alcLabel .\\n    FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?alcLabel)), \\"alc\\"))\\n  }\\n\\n  # MPC endpoint reference (endpoint URL and optional DB name)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcName . }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zoneLabel ?propLabel"\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 7, 39, 34, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
